{"tid":334044,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"擺渡人（好充實）","createTime":"2017-07-24T11:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T14:41:23.000Z","uid":99573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c56a3d2cfbae740ccf02ef6057ef0d78fb757b7d","tid":334044,"uid":99573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:14:00.000Z","msg":"睇左頭二十分鐘已經抖唔到氣，成套戲就係不斷地高潮同出配樂，d情節仲濃縮過雞精。<br />\n馬力既重新振作就得「一場演唱會」；江潔同小玉比試就無厘頭（不過答案果段就還好）；而管春同毛毛就好似青春劇咁，風格千變萬化。被擺渡既人全部都圍繞住愛情，用成四五個故事講埶着。<br />\n「不過其實又幾多睇既」"},{"pid":"f2143acc6ea6eada4695af2dbcf8da907090ef2e","tid":334044,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:21:29.000Z","msg":"一段文可以錯幾多隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed37a9e15e4cf5f79cf198d33fab2f4c50b58d79","tid":334044,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"公司廿周年整套咁嘅野都幾尷尬，不過為咗cap水就由佢啦"},{"pid":"5eb0702f9b5c08ebb25aab629d4cdd51effc9163","tid":334044,"uid":49178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:33:19.000Z","msg":"不了 同書差太完<br />\n管春同毛毛喺書到 明明係經歷左背叛 等待 原諒 錯過 管春最後一邊喊一邊講 你累了嗎 完完全全表達到當中既等待同原諒<br />\n電影管春變咗個白痴仔 又咩唔識英文又去左南極 又咩天下第一餅<br />\n<br />\n個酒吧馬拉松最尾我反而覺得唔好 講得太白 好似書咁 直接飲完 個臭雞輸左 馬力送佢番去 又比人見到曬 咁先好 一切盡在心中 唔洗講出口"},{"pid":"fd26c8c280731fc775ff631f419ce7390a3e2be9","tid":334044,"uid":49815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:36:36.000Z","msg":"你得不到，是因為不屬於你；放不下，因為你不甘心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3665aabeea5f7a8a2c54d6e5edc4413155d6149","tid":334044,"uid":111571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:51:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"078eeecc231489eb9545872580aec5701daf17b1","tid":334044,"uid":49815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梁朝偉先日拍埋d垃圾片，佢真係差過張家輝</blockquote><br />\n佢呢套戲做到有啲似韓城攻略既佢"},{"pid":"d7a08c2f7a49b4bf1e99d4d7c4770ffcf8d9807c","tid":334044,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:07:17.000Z","msg":"呢套根本係拎王大導個名cap水<br />\n唔睇名都唔知係王家衛拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2223115b7151514f77072f2dd7ebe7886e0c433","tid":334044,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢套根本係拎王大導個名cap水<br />\n唔睇名都唔知係王家衛拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但好似真係王大導指導大部份戲，<br />\n鮑德熹金像獎話連擺機位都要問過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefbbc3991c478110ac51bef8038c1647cac2f7d","tid":334044,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:41:23.000Z","msg":"都陪你渡過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}